summary: This is a save of a character I made using my mod that allows High Elves to have more \"human\" like facial
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds all nose, eyes and mouth selections to the Dark Elf race in the character creator and CK.

**My other mods**
Facial Features for Dark Elves: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=11394

If you use this mod please upload pictures of your characters so people can see your creations. . . and don\'t forget to endorse. Thanks
author: althekoolkid
